{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1142,"text":"So, my name is Roger Doiron,"},{"time":2921,"text":"and I have a subversive plot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5366,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":7642,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8970,"text":"It is so subversive, in fact,"},{"time":11344,"text":"that it has the potential\nto radically alter the balance of power,"},{"time":15492,"text":"not only in our own country,"},{"time":17571,"text":"but in the entire world."},{"time":19824,"text":"Now I realize, I'm sounding --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21403,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":22440,"text":"a little bit like Dr. Evil now."},{"time":25220,"text":"I understand that."},{"time":26416,"text":"But trust me -- we have very,\nvery little in common."},{"time":29226,"text":"His plots are all about\ndestruction and secrecy,"},{"time":32911,"text":"whereas my plots are about\ncreation and openness."},{"time":35963,"text":"In fact, my plot can only work"},{"time":38496,"text":"if I share it with as many\npeople as possible."},{"time":41230,"text":"So I'm going to share it with you now,"},{"time":43110,"text":"but you have to promise me\nyou're going to share it in turn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45972,"text":"So here it is."},{"time":47293,"text":"Huh. That's not so good, is it?"},{"time":49704,"text":"There's nothing particularly radical\nor revolutionary about a patch of grass."},{"time":53443,"text":"What starts to get interesting\nis when we turn it into this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57759,"text":"Now, I would like to suggest to you all"},{"time":60090,"text":"that gardening is a subversive activity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63175,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64720,"text":"Think about this:\nfood is a form of energy."},{"time":68578,"text":"It's what our body runs on,"},{"time":69952,"text":"but it's also a form of power."},{"time":72428,"text":"And when we encourage people\nto grow some of their own food,"},{"time":75866,"text":"we're encouraging them\nto take power into their hands,"},{"time":79178,"text":"power over their diet,"},{"time":81177,"text":"power over their health"},{"time":83048,"text":"and some power over their pocketbooks."},{"time":86090,"text":"So I think that's quite subversive,\nbecause we're also necessarily"},{"time":89703,"text":"talking about taking that power away"},{"time":92654,"text":"from someone else,"},{"time":94496,"text":"from other actors in society\nthat currently have power"},{"time":97732,"text":"over food and health."},{"time":99181,"text":"You can think about\nwho those actors might be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102627,"text":"I also look at gardening\nas a sort of healthy gateway drug,"},{"time":106515,"text":"you might say, to other forms\nof food freedom."},{"time":109903,"text":"It's not long after you plant a garden"},{"time":112484,"text":"that you start to say, \"Hey,\nI need to start to learn how to cook.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":115984,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":118508,"text":"\"You know, I might want\nto look into food preservation"},{"time":121316,"text":"or I might want to look up\nwhere my local farmer's market"},{"time":124636,"text":"is located in my town.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":127076,"text":"Now the other thing, of course,\nwith planting a garden,"},{"time":130004,"text":"especially a garden\nin front of a white house"},{"time":132650,"text":"and on a sunny south lawn,"},{"time":134628,"text":"is you never know who you might influence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136881,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":138493,"text":"Now, I'm not exactly sure\nwhat my white house garden's influence"},{"time":142196,"text":"was on the First Lady's,"},{"time":144572,"text":"but I can tell you this:"},{"time":145839,"text":"she's had an enormous influence on me"},{"time":148064,"text":"since planting hers."},{"time":149347,"text":"Now it hasn't been --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":150789,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154116,"text":"it hasn't been in the area of fashion."},{"time":156217,"text":"I understand that she's just\nin a completely different league there,"},{"time":160338,"text":"and I'm not even trying to compete."},{"time":163037,"text":"But she's really inspired me\nto think much more boldly"},{"time":166489,"text":"about the role that I want to have\nin the garden movement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170189,"text":"And so this is sort of\nwhat I'm aspiring to here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173143,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":175687,"text":"Now, pretty modest, right?"},{"time":178472,"text":"I like this picture."},{"time":179682,"text":"I think it sort of captures me well,"},{"time":181491,"text":"not that I have any\ndivine connections whatsoever,"},{"time":183858,"text":"but I like my facial expression there,"},{"time":186643,"text":"because, if I've got\na worried look on my face,"},{"time":189404,"text":"it's not simply because I've got\n20 pounds of squash over my head,"},{"time":193096,"text":"but it's because I've got some\npretty heavy topics on my mind."},{"time":196679,"text":"And I want to share some of those\nwith you right now,"},{"time":199231,"text":"starting off in the form of a very\nshort video I've produced for you,"},{"time":203154,"text":"which is my best effort\nto sum up the history of gastronomy"},{"time":207565,"text":"in about 15 seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210806,"text":"(\"Also sprach Zarathustra\" plays)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226930,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":232862,"text":"So, here we are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234368,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239280,"text":"Now, that's a funny little clip,"},{"time":240841,"text":"but it'd be even funnier\nif it weren't so tragic"},{"time":243310,"text":"and if it weren't so true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244650,"text":"The reality is that we are in the midst\nof an obesity epidemic,"},{"time":248557,"text":"and it's not simply\nlimited to our country."},{"time":251004,"text":"It's spreading around the world right now."},{"time":253206,"text":"And in a sort of parallel universe,"},{"time":255161,"text":"we're also seeing\nthat hunger is on the rise."},{"time":258021,"text":"Over 900 million people\nright now are affected by it."},{"time":261655,"text":"That's three times the population\nof the United States."},{"time":264561,"text":"But at the same time,"},{"time":265861,"text":"world food prices are rising"},{"time":268571,"text":"and world population is rising\nand is set to reach 10 billion people"},{"time":273271,"text":"by the end of the century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274867,"text":"Now, another thing about the population\nis we know that it's increasing,"},{"time":278273,"text":"but a lot of us don't realize\nthat it's also changing."},{"time":281609,"text":"There's a fundamental shift taking place."},{"time":283697,"text":"As of 2007, we went from being\na primarily rural planet"},{"time":288544,"text":"to being a primarily urban one,"},{"time":290652,"text":"and that has implications\nfor how we're going to feed these people,"},{"time":293820,"text":"how we're going to get the food\nto the people in the cities."},{"time":297595,"text":"Now, I imagine that there are\nsome Stephen King fans"},{"time":300140,"text":"in the audience here,"},{"time":301334,"text":"and I'm one of them."},{"time":302963,"text":"But I can tell you, I haven't read\nanything scarier than this here,"},{"time":307342,"text":"and that's this statistic:"},{"time":308692,"text":"in order to keep up\nwith the growing population,"},{"time":312380,"text":"we're going to need to grow more food\nover the course of the next 50 years"},{"time":316680,"text":"than we have grown over the course\nof the past 10,000 years combined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322326,"text":"What makes this even more challenging"},{"time":324409,"text":"is that we're going to need\nto grow all this food with less,"},{"time":328457,"text":"and when I say less,"},{"time":329911,"text":"I mean a number of things."},{"time":331234,"text":"Less oil, for example."},{"time":332995,"text":"Most reputable geologists believe\nthat we've already reached"},{"time":336380,"text":"peak oil production in the world."},{"time":338318,"text":"Now, you might not think in terms\nof oil and food as being linked,"},{"time":342492,"text":"but there's a very strong link, in fact."},{"time":344790,"text":"It takes 10 calories of fossil fuel energy"},{"time":348425,"text":"in our highly industrialized food system"},{"time":350747,"text":"in order to produce\none calorie of food energy."},{"time":354294,"text":"We'll also need to grow\nmore food with less water."},{"time":357257,"text":"These three images come from three\nvery different parts of the planet,"},{"time":360568,"text":"but they all tell the same story\nof catastrophic drought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364881,"text":"We'll also need to grow\nmore food with less farmland."},{"time":367753,"text":"Here, the pressures differ\nfrom one place to the next."},{"time":371180,"text":"In the Global South,\nwe're seeing desertification,"},{"time":374111,"text":"whereas in the north,\nwe're seeing suburban sprawl."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377561,"text":"We'll also have to grow more food\nwith less climate stability"},{"time":381308,"text":"and less genetic diversity."},{"time":383623,"text":"Now, this is really important."},{"time":385130,"text":"We need our genetic varieties"},{"time":387091,"text":"because they're a sort of insurance policy\nagainst climate change."},{"time":392014,"text":"We heard earlier today"},{"time":393226,"text":"\"not putting all of our eggs\nin one basket.\""},{"time":395519,"text":"Well, we shouldn't be doing\nthe same with our tomatoes, either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399155,"text":"We're also going to need\nto grow more food with less time."},{"time":403358,"text":"Now here, I'm not simply talking\nabout the ticking time bomb"},{"time":406789,"text":"that is the global population."},{"time":408514,"text":"I'm talking about\nthe amount of time we all have"},{"time":411707,"text":"in order to put\na decent meal on the table."},{"time":414264,"text":"And that \"31\" figure there\nis not something arbitrary."},{"time":417546,"text":"That's the average amount of time\nthe American family spends"},{"time":421309,"text":"preparing, eating and cleaning up\nafter meals per day."},{"time":426824,"text":"31 minutes."},{"time":428056,"text":"So somewhere in there, we're going\nto need to also fit in growing food."},{"time":432434,"text":"Alright?"},{"time":433616,"text":"And I think we do need to do that,"},{"time":435465,"text":"but that's also going to mean\nthat somewhere along the way,"},{"time":438336,"text":"something's going to have to give."},{"time":440009,"text":"So it sort of leaves us feeling like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443007,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":444223,"text":"You know?"},{"time":445411,"text":"It's time to leave town\nor even perhaps leave planets."},{"time":447995,"text":"But where do we go?"},{"time":449570,"text":"Where do we go\nwhen we only have one planet?"},{"time":451703,"text":"And where do we go\nwhere the going gets tough?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454348,"text":"Well, if we were to listen to a lot\nof our political leaders over the years,"},{"time":458263,"text":"we would simply go shopping."},{"time":459743,"text":"Right?"},{"time":461139,"text":"Because we have this unwavering belief,"},{"time":463657,"text":"especially in American political culture,"},{"time":465635,"text":"that we can shop our way\nout of just about any problem."},{"time":469114,"text":"But the reality is something different."},{"time":471139,"text":"We're not going to solve\nour food problems and our health problems"},{"time":474658,"text":"simply by switching from regular Coke"},{"time":477953,"text":"to some future green iteration thereof."},{"time":482451,"text":"And although the large food companies\nwould like us to believe"},{"time":487666,"text":"that we can give our children\nall of the vitamins, minerals"},{"time":491352,"text":"and immunity-building\nsubstances that they need"},{"time":493843,"text":"without even leaving\nthe chocolatey cereal aisle --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":496529,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":497593,"text":"the truth is something quite different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499699,"text":"Now, what's become\neven more troublesome of late"},{"time":502511,"text":"is that even the foods\nthat ought to be healthy aren't always so,"},{"time":507487,"text":"and we're starting to lose confidence\nin our food system, I think."},{"time":510713,"text":"The bigger it becomes\nand the more complex it becomes."},{"time":514048,"text":"And we've seen this time and time again."},{"time":515978,"text":"This is an image\nfrom the latest E. coli outbreak."},{"time":519633,"text":"In this case, it was in Europe,"},{"time":521328,"text":"and we think it was started\nwith bean sprouts, of all things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527017,"text":"So we have this sort of\nshopper's dilemma right now."},{"time":530034,"text":"We have all of these different foods --"},{"time":532164,"text":"30,000 foods in the average\nbig-box grocery store --"},{"time":536354,"text":"but we have less confidence\nin those foods,"},{"time":538839,"text":"and we have less confidence in the actors"},{"time":541430,"text":"that are putting those foods\non the shelves."},{"time":544192,"text":"I think we need to redefine\nwhat good food is."},{"time":547011,"text":"This is an interesting image\nfrom Berlin, Germany,"},{"time":549539,"text":"where somebody started planting\nshopping carts and leaving them around."},{"time":552969,"text":"Those are potatoes, by the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":554845,"text":"But in addition to redefining\nwhat good food is,"},{"time":557428,"text":"I think we need to redefine\nour living spaces."},{"time":560015,"text":"Instead of seeing this as a yard,"},{"time":563186,"text":"we need to think of it more\nas like a full-service greengrocer."},{"time":566766,"text":"That's, in fact, my yard,\nand that's how I look at it."},{"time":569819,"text":"That's what we transformed our yard into,"},{"time":573040,"text":"and I think a really key\nmessage is this one:"},{"time":575395,"text":"gardens grow good food."},{"time":578330,"text":"And when I say good food,"},{"time":579930,"text":"I mean a number of different things."},{"time":581685,"text":"I mean food that is safe,"},{"time":583157,"text":"food that is healthy,"},{"time":584613,"text":"food that is absolutely gorgeous"},{"time":586578,"text":"and delicious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588319,"text":"Another important message is this one:"},{"time":590554,"text":"gardens grow healthy kids and families."},{"time":593327,"text":"Those happen to be my two youngest sons,"},{"time":595855,"text":"and they look healthy\nand they are healthy,"},{"time":598179,"text":"and I think it has to do with the fact\nthat they grew up in gardens"},{"time":602171,"text":"and they know where good food comes from."},{"time":604515,"text":"And in fact, they know how\nto grow some of it themselves."},{"time":608017,"text":"But in the current economy,\nI think it's key to get this message out,"},{"time":611457,"text":"that gardens also grow\nimportant economic savings for families."},{"time":616089,"text":"And you can pretty much\ntake my word on this one,"},{"time":618841,"text":"because in addition to crunching\nthe vegetables a couple of years ago,"},{"time":623590,"text":"my wife and I also crunched the numbers,"},{"time":625862,"text":"and we found out that at the end,"},{"time":628005,"text":"we had saved well over 2,000 dollars\nby growing our own food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633000,"text":"So you could be asking this question now:"},{"time":635186,"text":"If gardens grow all of these great things,\nhow do we grow more gardens?"},{"time":639465,"text":"That's, in fact, the question\nthat my organization,"},{"time":642150,"text":"Kitchen Gardens International,"},{"time":643644,"text":"is both asking and answering."},{"time":646213,"text":"And our answer is essentially this one:"},{"time":648278,"text":"we're going to need to leverage\nthe resources and power that we have,"},{"time":652392,"text":"the gardens and gardeners that we have,"},{"time":655065,"text":"in order to grow and inspire even more."},{"time":658492,"text":"And as I said before, you never know\nwho you might inspire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661882,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663655,"text":"Now if this campaign was successful,"},{"time":666516,"text":"I think it wasn't simply because we had\na visionary First Lady"},{"time":671139,"text":"taking up residence at the White House --"},{"time":673605,"text":"that certainly was a major part of it --"},{"time":675680,"text":"and it wasn't simply because we had\nsome celebrity chefs and authors"},{"time":678936,"text":"saying this would be a good idea to do."},{"time":681123,"text":"I think it was ultimately made possible"},{"time":683905,"text":"by the fact that there were\na lot of people who wanted it to happen."},{"time":687257,"text":"There was a movement that made it happen."},{"time":689469,"text":"And my organization tried\nto sort of channel some of that energy"},{"time":692845,"text":"of the movement"},{"time":694022,"text":"and direct it towards the White House."},{"time":696333,"text":"And we had a lot of luck"},{"time":697549,"text":"in terms of getting our message\nout there to the media."},{"time":700209,"text":"We had a petition on Facebook,\n110,000 signatures."},{"time":703755,"text":"We had viral images and videos,"},{"time":706226,"text":"and we did crazy things like\nsymbolically putting the White House lawn"},{"time":710088,"text":"up for sale on eBay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713141,"text":"But we need to do even more,"},{"time":714552,"text":"and what we're trying to do\nin my organization"},{"time":716787,"text":"is to connect people online,"},{"time":718152,"text":"but also to connect people in person."},{"time":720332,"text":"This is an image from a little\nholiday we invented"},{"time":723320,"text":"called \"World Kitchen Garden Day.\""},{"time":725313,"text":"It's at the end of August each year,"},{"time":727298,"text":"and it's just about bringing\npeople together in gardens"},{"time":729931,"text":"to learn from one another,"},{"time":731351,"text":"to experience a garden\nas a community experience."},{"time":734143,"text":"We also need to grow\nthe next generation of gardeners,"},{"time":736959,"text":"and we're doing that\nin the United States and abroad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740110,"text":"But there's still so much more\nthat needs to be done,"},{"time":743188,"text":"and I think this slide sort of captures\nwhere we need to go."},{"time":746229,"text":"We need a road map,"},{"time":747573,"text":"and I picked this slide for a reason."},{"time":749381,"text":"We've got a bike garden on the left"},{"time":751118,"text":"and a map of the Netherlands on the right."},{"time":753184,"text":"I was in the Netherlands early this year"},{"time":755196,"text":"and was absolutely amazed\nby the amount of bikes on the road;"},{"time":759192,"text":"26 percent of all trips taken\nin the Netherlands are by bicycle,"},{"time":762898,"text":"and it's gotten me thinking:"},{"time":764274,"text":"How do we get that happening\nin terms of food and gardens?"},{"time":767236,"text":"How would we get 26 percent of all produce\ncoming from backyard gardens?"},{"time":770986,"text":"That might sound like a lot,"},{"time":772681,"text":"because we're probably at about\ntwo percent at the most right now."},{"time":775864,"text":"But if you take into consideration"},{"time":777561,"text":"that at the peak of the victory garden\nmovement last century,"},{"time":780866,"text":"40 percent of all produce\nwas coming from gardens."},{"time":784173,"text":"We can get there again."},{"time":786171,"text":"And I think this is a really good start."},{"time":788159,"text":"The White House garden\nis certainly very inspirational."},{"time":791054,"text":"That's actually sort of a snapshot\nof what the garden looked like"},{"time":794246,"text":"when it was planted earlier this spring --"},{"time":796294,"text":"lots of diversity, lots of healthy crops."},{"time":799058,"text":"However, this is not a good representation"},{"time":802026,"text":"of our federal agriculture policy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803919,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":805504,"text":"If we were to take the model here,\nthe diagram of that particular garden,"},{"time":810207,"text":"and sort of transpose it\nonto our federal agriculture policy,"},{"time":814671,"text":"we'd get this:"},{"time":816759,"text":"billions of billions of dollars\ngoing to support"},{"time":819750,"text":"just a handful of commodity crops"},{"time":823032,"text":"with just that tiny little bit at the top\nfor fruits and vegetables."},{"time":826819,"text":"This is scandalous. This is scandalous."},{"time":829463,"text":"We need to do something about this."},{"time":833774,"text":"I think one place we could start\nis we could look at the tax code."},{"time":837517,"text":"We're already using the tax code\nto encourage green transport"},{"time":841315,"text":"and green shelter."},{"time":842703,"text":"Why not green food?"},{"time":844070,"text":"We're in the midst now of talking\nabout another stimulus package."},{"time":847368,"text":"Why not a garden stimulus package?"},{"time":850146,"text":"Why not?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":851346,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":859395,"text":"In terms of other things\nthat we need to be doing,"},{"time":861863,"text":"we need to move down to the local level"},{"time":863825,"text":"and we need to make sure\nthat gardens are legal."},{"time":866300,"text":"This is an illegal garden.\nAt least it was."},{"time":868411,"text":"It's from Michigan earlier this year."},{"time":870292,"text":"It was planted by a woman,\na mother of four,"},{"time":873243,"text":"and she nearly faced\na 93-day jail sentence"},{"time":876532,"text":"because she planted it in her front yard."},{"time":879175,"text":"We still have laws from the 20th century."},{"time":883344,"text":"We need to bring our codes up\nto the realities that we are facing now."},{"time":889082,"text":"We need to figure out also\nnew ways of getting people into gardens,"},{"time":892875,"text":"people who don't have yards."},{"time":895223,"text":"I think we also need to set\ngarden entrepreneurism free,"},{"time":899008,"text":"and I'm happy to say, as a Mainer,"},{"time":901266,"text":"that we are leading the way in this area."},{"time":903653,"text":"Earlier this year, a number of Maine towns"},{"time":906134,"text":"passed local food sovereignty laws"},{"time":908549,"text":"that allow town residents\nto not only grow food"},{"time":911509,"text":"where they want to grow it"},{"time":912854,"text":"but to also sell it\nthe way they want to sell it"},{"time":915751,"text":"and to the people they want to sell it to."},{"time":917862,"text":"I think that's an incentive."},{"time":919713,"text":"There are a lot of gardeners out there"},{"time":921571,"text":"that would be interested in scaling up\ntheir production if they could,"},{"time":924952,"text":"if they had a financial incentive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927247,"text":"I also think that we need to examine"},{"time":929452,"text":"the composition of the movement right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932478,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":934774,"text":"If the movement were a 1960s beach flick,"},{"time":938263,"text":"it would be \"Where The Boys Aren't.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":940057,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":941098,"text":"So I'm going to take you to task, guys."},{"time":943351,"text":"It's not right and it's not fair\nthat the burden of this responsibility --"},{"time":947680,"text":"feeding our country and the world --"},{"time":949435,"text":"should be with the women."},{"time":950704,"text":"OK?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":951902,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":955143,"text":"And I'm going to challenge the women"},{"time":956948,"text":"to come up with really clever,\ncreative ways of getting guys"},{"time":959940,"text":"into the gardens, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961229,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":962600,"text":"Perhaps wearing a bathing suit?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":964216,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":966728,"text":"But beyond that, I think we need\nto reexamine the infrastructure"},{"time":970272,"text":"that we have in place for gardens."},{"time":971972,"text":"I think we need to create\nnew infrastructure."},{"time":974279,"text":"And this is one of the things\nmy organization is working on right now,"},{"time":978077,"text":"sort of a local communications\ninfrastructure, very place-based,"},{"time":982985,"text":"that allows people in the same area\nto connect with one another"},{"time":986675,"text":"and to help each other out."},{"time":989128,"text":"I think we're lacking this\nat the moment --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":991260,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":992889,"text":"but we can do it."},{"time":994261,"text":"The technology is certainly there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996303,"text":"In addition to that, I think we need\nanother type of infrastructure."},{"time":999578,"text":"It would be good if we could\nall get together."},{"time":1001781,"text":"I think if we've learned anything\nthrough the TED experience,"},{"time":1005124,"text":"it's that there is power\nwhen we bring people together,"},{"time":1007884,"text":"and I think we need to bring people\ntogether at the local level as well."},{"time":1011321,"text":"And I think we can take some inspiration\nfrom a previous movement,"},{"time":1014543,"text":"which was the grange movement,"},{"time":1016004,"text":"a rural movement which brought farmers\ntogether in a single building"},{"time":1020581,"text":"to meet and to recreate\nand learn how to become better farmers."},{"time":1024035,"text":"I think we need a network"},{"time":1025993,"text":"of suburban granges now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029916,"text":"I think one of the last\nthings that we need"},{"time":1032110,"text":"is to not lose the fun of food."},{"time":1034828,"text":"Food is at its best when it's delicious\nbut shared as part of a community,"},{"time":1040311,"text":"and I think that gardens can get\nsome of that community vibe back as well."},{"time":1044722,"text":"So I'm going to leave with one last video,"},{"time":1047338,"text":"and I'm going to revisit the short video\nthat I showed you before,"},{"time":1051402,"text":"but I'm going to suggest\nan alternative ending."},{"time":1055458,"text":"And I think this ending\nis well within our reach,"},{"time":1058237,"text":"but it's really going to require\nthat we all pull together."},{"time":1061121,"text":"So here's the new history of gastronomy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1065750,"text":"(\"Also sprach Zarathustra\" plays)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1082456,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1104944,"text":"(Applause and cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1113692,"text":"Thank you very much.\nThank you all. Thank you."}]}]}